#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.logical_or.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.logical\\_or"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or:1 of
msgid "Compute the truth value of x1 OR x2 element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算 x1 或 x2 的真值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or:3
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or:6 of
msgid ""
"Logical OR is applied to the elements of `x1` and `x2`. They have to be "
"of the same shape."
msgstr "逻辑或运算应用于 `x1` 和 `x2` 的元素。它们必须具有相同的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or:9 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or:14 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or:19 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- Boolean result with the same shape as `x1` and `x2` of the "
"logical OR operation on elements of `x1` and `x2`."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 布尔结果，形状与 `x1` 和 `x2` 相同，表示对 `x1` 和 `x2` 元素进行"
"逻辑或运算的结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.logical_or.logical_or:23 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`logical_and`, :py:obj:`logical_not`, :py:obj:`logical_xor`, "
":py:obj:`bitwise_or`"
msgstr ""

